# R3F Architecture Archive

> **ARCHIVED**: This document describes the legacy React Three Fiber architecture that was replaced by deck.gl in the DECK-MIGRATE-001 migration.

## Overview

The original MMS Canvas used React Three Fiber (R3F) for WebGL rendering with a custom LOD system implemented via InstancedMesh.

